General.Name: Eticket4
General.Description: Eticket4 is a blockchain-based P2P event ticket distribution and exchange platform with powerful analytical tools and an automated flexible loyalty program. ET4 is an Ethereum-based ERC20 token used for all transactions within the platform.

ICO.Description:
Eticket4 is a blockchain-based P2P event ticket distribution and exchange platform with powerful analytical tools and an automated flexible loyalty program. ET4 is an Ethereum-based ERC20 token used for all transactions within the platform.

Team:

  • Daniil Kruchinin: Cofounder / Marketing 
  • Dmitry Fedorovich: Cofounder / Chief Developer
  • Jevgenijs Vainsteins: Strategy director advisor 
  • Ilya Stechkin: Adviser  

The Eticket4 ICO will start on the 30th of February and will last until the 23rd of March. The ICO token allocations represents  54% of the total token supply and will be available for a 0.001 ETH starting price. The ICO funding target/cap is set at 13800 ETH. 

Token Reserve Split (54%):

  • 20% - Eticket4 team,
  • 10% - Private offer,
  • 10% - Mining,
  • 7% - Growth fund,
  • 4% - Advisers,
  • 3% - Bounty

The ET4 ICO features a bonus and bounty campaign.

Bonus Structure:

  • 5 Days: 8%
  • 6 - 10 Days: 6%
  • 11 - 20 Days: 4%
  • 21 - 30 Days: 2%
